{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be rustic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cyber Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a1931;\n            --secondary-color: #185a9d;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #000000;\n            --accent-color: #2b3a42;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        section p {\n            text-align: justify;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services-list li {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureGuard Cyber Solutions</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At SecureGuard Cyber Solutions, we are dedicated to safeguarding your digital assets with robust and innovative cybersecurity strategies. In a world increasingly reliant on technology, protecting your data, systems, and reputation is paramount. Our team of seasoned professionals brings a wealth of experience and a proactive approach to identify, mitigate, and defend against the ever-evolving landscape of cyber threats.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <ul class=\"services-list\">\n                <li>Risk Assessment & Management</li>\n                <li>Network Security</li>\n                <li>Data Encryption & Protection</li>\n                <li>Incident Response</li>\n                <li>Vulnerability Testing</li>\n                <li>Security Awareness Training</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cyber Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}